              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17474563834557200790">This book is beyond any possible rating. It is, I believe, the book that says the definitive word about holocaust and about human cruelty. After this, nothing else can be said and no explanation can be given to what men can do to other men. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


